reviewText: A must-have for any longtime Lahaina resident.  This dvd really brought back a lot of great memories for me.  I'm so glad I bought this.
Awesome to watch. I bought this to show my son when he gets older. I want him to see how much his home town has change. I want him to stay close to his roots.
Eddie Kamai did a very nice job in presenting this DVD about the history of Lahaina.....Love this town, now I know more history....A must buy for Maui lovers!

Viewing Lahaina: Waves of Change brought back a lot of old memories and the tradition of growing up in nostalgic Maui.  Local customs, language, and the real old aloha hospitality attitude.  Another excellent video by Eddie Kamae!

If you love Hawaii.... you need to buy this video!
If you want to get a glimpse of the past and see and hear how old Lahaina was.... you need to buy this video!
Even if you might get a little chicken skin in places ;-)

Mahalo Nui Eddie Kamae for a great tour!
